OL,5, The boss of P&O Ferries has been given 
OL,6, "one final opportunity" to reemploy    
OL,7, sacked staff on their previous salaries
OL,8, by Transport Secretary Grant Shapps.   
OL,10,FIn a letter, Mr Shapps again urged     
OL,11,FPeter Hebblethwaite to reverse his     
OL,12,Fdecision to sack 800 seafarers.        
OL,14,FIf not, he said the government's plans 
OL,15,Fto make it illegal for ferry firms to  
OL,16,Fpay less than the minimum wage, would  
OL,17,Flikely force him to do so.             
OL,19,FP&O Ferries said sacking workers was   
OL,20,Fnot just about saving money on wages.  
